          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Measured gamma-spectra   from   K-39(g,pg')Ar-38  and",
                " K-39(g,ng')K-38 reactions induced by  bremsstrahlung",
                " gamma-quanta with 32 MeV end-point energy.",
                "Integrated cross sections of  photonucleon  reactions",
                " on  K-39  with formation of final nuclei in separate",
                " states were determined based on an analysis  of  the",
                " experimental data.",
                "It is found that  for  this  nuclei  the  semi-direct",
                " decay  probability  for GDR in the (gamma,p) channel",
                " amounts to 0.46 - 0.56 and the (gamma,n) it is 0.95."
              ]
            }
          ],
